    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(ST) In Christi nomine. Otto gracia Dei imperator augustus, anno imperii
                        eius sex[to], mense aprilis, indicione decima. Constat me <persName><name
                                ref="Lanfredus">Lanfredus</name></persName> fil(ius) quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Waldegarius">Walcarii</name></persName> de <rs
                            key="#Vici">vico</rs>
                        <placeName>Mapello</placeName> accepisem sicuti et in presencia testium
                        manifestus sum qui accepi ad te <persName><name ref="Adrebertus"
                                >Adrevertus</name></persName> fil(ius) bone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Andreas">Andrei</name></persName> de eodem [v]ico Mapello <rs
                            key="#Price">argentum denarios bonos solidos nove</rs>, finitum precium
                        sic inter nobis convenit pro <rs key="#Forests">silva</rs>
                        <rs key="#Chestnuts">casteneta</rs>
                        <rs key="#Petiae">pecia</rs> unacum area in qua estat [...] ar[bo]ris
                        castenei de super habente, que habere visus [sum in suprascripto vico et <rs
                            key="#Fundi">fun]do</rs>
                        <geogName ref="#estates/4133" key="#Fundi #Petiae #Forests #Chestnuts"
                            >Mapello</geogName>, locus ubi dicitur Casteneto <persName><name
                                ref="Teudebertus">Teoper[ti</name></persName>; coerit e]i da mane
                            <rs key="#Roads">via</rs>, da meridie <rs key="#Churches"><orgName
                                ref="#juridical_persons/188" key="#Confinia">Sancti
                                Alexandri</orgName></rs>, da sera <persName ref="#people/4810"
                            key="#Confinia">Lantrude</persName>, da monte <persName><name
                                ref="Gherardus">Geriardi</name></persName> et est area ex ipsa silva
                        per mensura <rs key="#Size">iusta tabulas quinn[quaginta</rs> ... Et] si
                        amplius inventum fuerit infra suprascriptes coerencies [quam ut supra
                        mensura legitur, in presente majneat vind(icione) pro suprascripto precium.
                        Que autem suprascripta sil[v]a et area eius, qualiter superius venundavi,
                        cum superiore et inferiore, cum [ingressora] et accessione sua presenti die
                        in tua qui supra emtori meo et cui tu [dederis vestr]isque heredibus
                        persistat potestatem, iure proprietario nomine habendum [et facien]dumd
                        exinde quicquit volueritis sine omni mea qui supra vinditori et heredibus
                        meis contradicione. Quidem spondeo adque promito me ego qui supra vinditor
                        cum [meis heredibus tibi qui supra] emtori meo et cui tu dederis vestrisque
                        heredibus suprascriptam vind(icionem) ad [implere et ab omni
                        cont]rad(icente) hominem defensare. Et si defendere non potuerimus aut si
                        contra hac carta agere quesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum
                        </rs>vobis predicta [v]ind(icione) restituamus in eodem loco; quia sic inter
                        nobis convenit. Actum Mapello. Signum + manus suprascripto Lanfredi qui hac
                        carta fieri rogavit. Signum ++++ manibus <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Andreas">Andrei</name></persName> fil(ii) quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Aribertus">Ariverti</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudaldus"
                            >Teodaldi</name></persName> filii quondam <persName><name ref="Getadus"
                                >Getadi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Gisbertus">Giseverti</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Thomas">Tomadi</name></persName> [...] seu <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Alexander">Alexandri</name></persName> de
                        Mapello <rs key="#Witness">testibus</rs>. (ST) <persName
                            key="#Notary #Judge"><name ref="Senepertus">Senepertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> domni
                        imperatoris scripsi, postradita compievi et dedi.</ab>
